# Research: EdTech School Connect Web Portal
slug: edtech-school-connect-web-portal
date: 2026-06-15

---

## 1. Domain and Competitor Context

### The Client's Posting
- An MVP-stage school-parent communication portal
- PHP mandatory, JS/HTML5 nice-to-have
- Real-time updates on student performance and activities
- Bidirectional school-parent communication
- 1-3 month engagement, intermediate level, hourly

### Competitor Products (the visual inspiration sources named in the plan)

**ClassDojo** (classdojo.com)
- Color palette: #1565C0 (deep blue primary), #00BCD4 (teal accent), white backgrounds
- Typography: clean sans-serif, rounded for student-facing content
- Layout: sidebar navigation, card-based feeds, avatar-heavy (teacher/student photos)
- UX: activity feed is dominant center-stage; messaging is right-panel or modal
- Notable: strong color-coded badges per category (green=academic, orange=behavior, blue=event)
- Mobile-first: bottom tab bar on mobile
- Tone: warm, encouraging, not clinical

**ParentSquare** (parentsquare.com)
- Color palette: #0078D4 (Microsoft-style blue), clean white cards, light gray (#F5F5F5) bg
- Typography: Inter-family or similar, dense but readable
- Layout: timeline/feed dominant; teachers have a compose panel at top
- Notable: unread count badges on every inbox item; category filtering in the feed
- Tone: professional, district-level feel, less "fun" than ClassDojo

**Seesaw** (web.seesaw.me)
- Color palette: #1A73E8 (Google blue lineage), #34A853 (green), #FBBC04 (yellow), #EA4335 (red)
- Typography: clean, accessible, Inter or Roboto
- Layout: left sidebar (icon + label pattern), content fills remaining space
- Notable: portfolio/journal metaphor; grade cards with percentage bars; teacher compose at top of feed
- Tone: creative, portfolio-centric, visual

### The Plan's Chosen Design Direction (already set by planner)
The plan synthesizes these three into a bespoke design. No further color research needed.
Confirmed values from plan.md:

| Token        | Value     | Use                               |
|--------------|-----------|-----------------------------------|
| Primary      | #1A56DB   | Buttons, active nav, links        |
| Primary Dark | #1E429F   | Hover states                      |
| Accent       | #0E9F6E   | Success badges, positive metrics  |
| Warning      | #E3A008   | Attendance alerts, caution        |
| Danger       | #E02424   | Overdue, failing grades           |
| Bg           | #F9FAFB   | Page background                   |
| Card         | #FFFFFF   | Cards, panels                     |
| Border       | #E5E7EB   | Card borders, dividers            |
| Text Primary | #111827   | Headings, body                    |
| Text Muted   | #6B7280   | Labels, timestamps                |

Typography:
- Heading: "Nunito" (Google Fonts) -- rounded, friendly, education-appropriate
- Body: "Inter" (Google Fonts) -- clean, readable at small sizes
- Google Fonts import URL: https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Nunito:wght@600;700;800&display=swap

