## 2. CDN Dependencies

### Chart.js (for radar chart in Performance view)
- CDN: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.0/dist/chart.umd.min.js
- Radar chart config: 6 axes (Math, English, Science, History, Art, PE)
- Scale: 0-100
- Fill enabled, semi-transparent area
- Colors: use Primary (#1A56DB) with 0.2 alpha fill

### No other CDN dependencies needed
- JWT is handled server-side (PyJWT on Flask)
- No React, no build step -- vanilla JS modules via type="module" or inline script tags
- All DOM manipulation is vanilla

